	   <tr><td colspan=2>YOU ARE COMPLETELY WRONG CETUS. Humans get NO exp. bonus over the other races that magicians can be. They level at the exact same speed. I said in my magician guide for NEWBIES to start out as high-elves or gnomes. As in characters that have never played the game before or only have one other low level character. Gnomes and High-elves are the best race for newbies becuase they are the two races that magicians can choose that have night vision and aren't evil. Also, high elves and gnomes start on the continent of Feydwer which is MUCH better for a newbie. Less danger than on all the other continents. Trust me, I know what I am talking about. Stop trying to think you know more or know better than a master magician. My guide, especially the 2nd one I wrote that added more stuff, is very good. Any newbie would be MUCH better off after reading it.<br><br>Zuranthium/Corpusnuntia/Divineshadow/Plantmaster/Sunsong/Natalos/Naltec<br><br>Player of many characters on the Nameless server.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
